The paper deals with the problem of assumptions refinement in the context of unrealizable specifications for reactive systems. This problem is related to logic and automated reasoning (cs.LO), programming languages (cs.PL), software engineering (cs.SE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and control systems (cs.SY). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
